SUBENT        F0546001   20251214   20260305   20260305       F105
BIB                  9         16
TITLE      Asymmetries in the angular correlations for the
           7Li+d - 2alpha+n reaction at Ed from 0.8 MeV to 1.2 MeV
AUTHOR     (V.D'Amico,G.Fazio,S.Jannelli,F.Mezzanares,R.Potenza)
INSTITUTE  (2ITYMES,2ITYCAT)
REFERENCE  (J,NCL,13,489,1975)
DETECTOR   (SIBAR)
SAMPLE     A natural Li target, 0.5 mg/cm2 thick, evaporated on
           a polyvinilformal backing of 0.1 um, was used.
REL-REF    (N,,V.D'Amico+,J,NC/A,22,313,1974) - The absolute
           values of the cross-sections were obtained by the
           method reported in this ref.
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) Statistical error
           (DATA-ERR) Absolute error
HISTORY    (20020416C)
           (20251214U) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
           DATA-ERR1 -> DATA-ERR.
ENDBIB              16
COMMON               1          3
DATA-ERR
PER-CENT
  15.0
ENDCOMMON            3
